              %h6.h6.list__list-item-title UI Design
              %p Interactions, accessibility, responsive layouts and interfaces.
            %li.list__list-item.development
              .list__list-item-icon
              %h6.h6.list__list-item-title Development
              %p HTML, CSS and Sass, JS and React, mobile and cross-browser testing and support.

